{"word":"G622 - ἀπόλλυμι - apóllymi - ap-ol'-loo-mee - Destroy","slug":"G622","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπόλλυμι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apóllymi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-ol'-loo-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Destroy"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - apollumi</b> - <i>ap-ol'-loo-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G3639\">G3639</a>; to <i>destroy</i> fully (reflexively to <i>perish</i>, or <i>lose</i>), literally or figuratively: - destroy, die, lose, mar, perish."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G623\">G623</a>, <a href=\"#/G684\">G684</a>"}]}